### Stage 13: Verification System (4-Layer)
- [ ] Layer 1: CNR number format validation
- [ ] Layer 2: OTP verification (already built in Stage 3)
- [ ] Layer 3: Advocate confirmation (optional, stores advocate details)
- [ ] Layer 4: Document upload + text extraction + matching
- [ ] Verification status progression: unverified → otp_verified → document_verified → fully_verified
- [ ] Test: Register → OTP verify → upload ID doc → verify status progression

